# Microservice implementation

## Workflow

1. Spec: `documentation/specifications/microservices/<group>/<service>/`
2. ADR: `documentation/ADR/index.md` — task-relevant only
3. Code: **target service only** — `application/<group>/<service>/` (if exists)
4. Implement via skill `microservice-defaults` + [reference.md](../skills/microservice-defaults/reference.md)

## Forbidden unless asked

- Exploratory repo sweep
- Opening `application/currency-valuables/currencies-crud` for standard CRUD/Kafka/Feign

Exception: new pattern missing from reference.md, or user asks to explore.

## Packages

`web/`, `service/`, `repository/`, `domain/`, `mapping/`, `kafka/`.

## Gradle

Plugins: `kotlin jvm 2.1.20`, `plugin.spring`, `spring-boot 3.5.14`, `dependency-management 1.1.7`, `com.vimpishsnorfle.database-test 0.1.0`, `com.vimpishsnorfle.jib 0.1.0`, `jacoco`. Java 21. Spring Cloud BOM `2025.0.2`.

Deps: `com.vimpishsnorfle.rest:*`, `jooq:*`, `messaging:*`, `crud-web-error-support`, `jooq-query-support`.

## REST

`@RestController` implements `V1*ControllerApi`; DTO from `*.model.*`. `GlobalExceptionHandler` extends `CrudExceptionHandlerSupport`.

## jOOQ

`@Repository` + `DSLContext`; static table/record imports; `applyListSort`, `ClockSupport`. No raw SQL.

## Kafka

Generated `*Consumer` or `Consumer<Message<Dto>>`. Producer uses generated messaging DTO.

## Feign

`@EnableFeignClients` on application class. Neighbor services: `interface XxxClient : V1*ControllerApi`.

## Tests

jacoco min `0.70`, `check` → verification. `@SpringBootTest` + `@Import(TestcontainersConfiguration)` + `@ActiveProfiles("test")`. Plugin `database-test`.

## Flyway

Migrations in `data-schemas/<group>/<schema>/src/main/sql/`, not in service.

